Learn About the Template Bot: Gather Info from User

The Gather info from user dialog is a shared dialog called from other dialogs to collect key information from the user. The dialog collects the user’s information by asking questions and filling variables with responses.

Both system entities and custom entities are used to capture user responses. System text entity captures a broad range of inputs, while custom entities help validate user responses before storing them in bot variables.
